And the burns on his face.

282
00:14:39,990 --> 00:14:41,250
Ok. Well,I'll check the manifest.

283
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:42,470
I'll see if his name turns up.

284
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:44,050
What about the voices?

285
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:44,970
What voices?

286
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,680
In your basement.

287
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:48,110
Didn't you hear them?

288
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:49,240
No,not really.

289
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:52,380
Wait a minute. You can hear
voices that melinda can't?

290
00:14:52,390 --> 00:14:54,180
That would make her
more powerful than you.

291
00:14:54,230 --> 00:14:55,540
No. That's just how it works.

292
00:14:55,570 --> 00:14:56,810
In the beginning,you get everything¡ª

