And then,eventually,you learn to tune
certain things out so you can function.

295
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:03,830
Whatever she's hearing,it's
probably coming from the tunnels.

296
00:15:03,850 --> 00:15:06,190
Do you still have that giant
hole in the wall in your basement?

297
00:15:06,230 --> 00:15:07,420
What tunnels?

298
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:09,060
Oh,you don't want to
know about the tunnels.

299
00:15:09,100 --> 00:15:10,700
Well,why not? What's under there?

300
00:15:10,730 --> 00:15:12,510
What's under there? More
like who's under there.

301
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:14,440
More accurately,who isn't under there.

302
00:15:14,470 --> 00:15:15,620
The amount of
trapped souls-

303
